body:
This PR introduces a realistic description of the inter-pixel cross-talk in the InnerTracker for 25x100 um^2 pixel cells (phase2 only) as determined by lab measurements on prototype chip+sensor assemblies. It affects the phase2 work flows with the following versions of the Tracker geometry: T5, T6, T7, T8, T9, T10. At the moment there is no evidence of x-talk in other pixel sizes. The work has been presented in Tracker Phase2 Simulation Meeting [*

[*]https://indico.cern.ch/event/768246/contributions/3199413/attachments/1746858/2828470/CMSSW_inter-pixel_cross-talk.pdf


